org.vadere.state.attributes.models

Class AttributesODEIntegrator

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.vadere.state.attributes.Attributes
      • org.vadere.state.attributes.models.AttributesODEIntegrator

  • public class AttributesODEIntegrator
extends Attributes
    Provides attributes for ODE integrators:
    IntegratorType, minStepSize, maxStepSize, absoluteTolerance, relativeTolerance. For methods without step size control, minStepSize and maxStepSize should be equal.
